  "body": "### What's your issue about?\r\nGas costs are changing in Istanbul! (See [EIP-1884](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1884), [EIP-2028](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-2028), and [EIP-2200](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-2200))\r\n\r\nHere's a preliminary table:\r\n\r\nName | Type | Address | Previous Cost | New Cost \r\n-- | -- | -- | -- | --\r\nSLOAD | Opcode | 0x54 | 200 | 800\r\nBALANCE | Opcode | 0x31 | 400 | 700\r\nEXTCODEHASH | Opcode | 0x3F | 400 | 700\r\nSSTORE | Opcode | 0x55 | 20000/5000 | TBD\r\nCALLDATALOAD | Opcode | 0x35 | 68 (per byte) | 16 (per byte)\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed?\r\nJust change the numbers when they're finalized\r\n\r\nNote: might be best to add this feature via #1230 ruleset switch so there it fails to compile under pre-Istanbul rules\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nEDIT: Removed [EIP-1108](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1108) because it was updating precompiles, not opcodes.",
