    "body": "Note: We don't have `ECADD` or `ECMUL` to contend with (per EIP-1108), and since we do the worst case with `SSTORE` it's not necessary to modify (per EIP-2200). `EXTCODEHASH` to be added via #1765. #1764 updates `SLOAD` and `BALANCE` (per EIP-1884).\r\n\r\nI couldn't figure out the best strategy to modify `CALLDATALOAD` costs, because they don't seem to be implemented in the standard way where the update would make sense.",
